abstract: This afternoon a telegram was received here from Liverpool which stated that the experiment of shipping peaches to England has proved a failure. The Ohio sailed from here twelve days ago with 2,450 crates of the fruit, sent out under a refrigerating process as a test. The steam-ship company did not send ice enough, and the supply gave out in three days after the vessel had left here.

abstract: SYRACUSE, N.Y., Sept. 16. It was publicly announced yesterday that the Democratic Convention to be held here to-day would commence its labors precisely at 12 o'clock. Punctuality, however, is not one of the virtues of a New-York City delegate to a Democratic gathering, and on account of the nonappearance of the representatives from the Metropolis the convention was not called to order until long after the hour mentioned.
